You may have heard of Joshua Tree National Park, but the popular travel destination is home to much more than meets the eye. 🏞️

Conservationist and nature photographer @ianshivephoto  recently explored the hidden Eagle Cliff Mine, one of the most well-maintained old mining homesteads in the park.

Experience the adventure: Discovery.com/secretmine

View the photo gallery: https://www.discovery.com/nature/explore-the-secret-mines-of-joshua-tree-pictures

#NatureInFocus

It's #NationalHoneyMonth, and these bees know where it's at. ✨

Having kids is difficult, but preparing the one meal for your young that will last them until next year is even harder! This female mason bee shows the signs that she has just created the ball of pollen and nectar that will see one of her larvae through the rest of the summer, until it can overwinter in a cocoon. 

📸: MarkHortonPhotography
